Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:52.22,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}全世界沉浸在愛戀中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:55.64,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}萬道光芒 照亮心房
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:58.98,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}我想瞭解你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:03.15,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:15.94,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}話不投機 有些後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:17.89,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}流下眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.03,0:01:23.22,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}心隨著急切的情感變亂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:30.53,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}調整情緒 想知道真實的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.56,0:01:36.28,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}執著於達成目的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:39.96,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}重要的事物在不覺間模糊 溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.11,0:01:45.68,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}今天是嶄新的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:51.11,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}全世界沉浸在愛戀中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:54.71,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}萬道光芒 照亮心房
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:58.05,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}我想瞭解一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.19,0:02:02.14,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}說給我聽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:05.77,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}一毫米的距離也覺得遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:08.84,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}匆匆走過的青春歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:13.11,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}不會忘 也忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:15.87,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}留下閃耀的一頁
